Description: This R package offers a comprehensive collection of variable clustering
 algorithms, featuring hierarchical, relocation-based, and qualitative variable
 approaches. Built using R6 object-oriented architecture, it provides interpretive
 tools such as visualizations, statistical summaries, and cluster assignments.
 The package also includes an interactive Shiny application for exploring and
 analyzing clustering results.
